  "description": "<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://tuan.hujiang.com/tuangou/p954/?source=499\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201307/c6497f4a-a0ee-47b0-be88-cce5977bf765_00.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t【琴声瑟瑟，优雅一生】319元抢原价399元沪江网校icanmusic轻松学古筝入门8月班。古筝&mdash;&mdash;清越悠扬，内涵深厚！其入门轻松极易掌握，适合各年龄层次音乐爱好者学习！中国古筝学院院长袁莎老师亲授，简化入门技巧，15课轻松掌握5大技法+8首名曲！进班送独家MIDI伴奏音乐，让学习充满乐趣！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">开团时间：</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">2013.7.12 &nbsp;16:30</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>团购平台：</strong><a href=\"http://tuan.hujiang.com/tuangou/p954/?source=499\" target=\"_blank\">&gt;&gt;沪江团购&lt;&lt;</a></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial; color: rgb(153, 0, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><strong>古筝学习知多少&mdash;&mdash;</strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t<strong>1、不受手型、年龄等先天条件限制：</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t学习手风琴，学员必须手大、手指长；学习长笛，学员必须嘴唇较薄；学习小提琴，学员必须左手小拇指够长&hellip;&hellip;而<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 51);\">学习古筝，完全不用顾虑自己的手指够不够长、够不够细、够不够灵活！</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t<strong>2、看似复杂，其实非常易学：</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t大家通常认为，弦类乐器极难入门，枯燥难懂的乐理知识、乏味机械的指法练习已经&ldquo;打败&rdquo;了一片曾信誓旦旦的音乐爱好者！然而，<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 51);\">古筝却属于弦类乐器中极易入门的乐器</span>，加之袁莎老师独门教学方式，<span>掌握古筝的入门技变得易如反掌！</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\">如果你倾心于</span><span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\">抑扬顿挫，柔柔似水的《春江花月夜》，</span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t<span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\">亦或是向往着潇洒不羁，侠情四溢的《沧海一声笑》，</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t<strong><span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\">再或者被《菊花台》、《青花瓷》这样的中国风流行曲所深深吸引。</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">古筝那如高山流水，通透落玉盘般的琴音一定会是你心中，最熟悉，最不可替代的那一声钟爱！</span></p>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial;\">\n\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 6px; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(62, 76, 144); border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px;\">\n\t\t<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\"><strong>课程详情</strong></span></p>\n\t<div class=\"video\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n\t\t<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n\t\t\t<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><strong>班级名称：</strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px;\">&nbsp;<font color=\"#075db3\">icanmusic轻松学古筝</font><font color=\"#075db3\">入门【8月通关班】</font></span>