an style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px;\"><br />\n\t\t\t</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px;\"><strong>课程特色：</strong><br />\n\t\t\t1. 古筝演奏家icanmusic金牌讲师袁莎老师亲自授课；<br />\n\t\t\t2.&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px;\">轻松易学，帮你掌握5大演奏技法+8首经典名曲；</span></span><br />\n\t\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px;\">3. 挑选经典名曲编成适合初学者的入门教材，入门不枯燥，练习很有趣；<br />\n\t\t\t4.&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px;\">高清视频课件清晰示范各种指法及弹奏技巧，不怕学不会；</span></span><br />\n\t\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px;\">5. 专业老师在线答疑课，学得愉快更要学得正确；<br />\n\t\t\t6. 课程配套伴奏音频及特色曲谱电子版提供。<br />\n\t\t\t课件支持苹果、安卓版移动网校，学习更加随心所欲！</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 6px; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(62, 76, 144); border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px;\">\n\t\t\t\t<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\"><strong>延续古典情怀，让梦想成真</strong></span></p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"http://tuan.hujiang.com/tuangou/p954/?source=499\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201307/c6497f4a-a0ee-47b0-be88-cce5977bf765_03.jpg\" /></a></p>\n\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t\t<strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\">每个人都有自己的中国古典情怀，每个人都有自己的中国古典音乐梦。</span></strong></p>\n\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t\t<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\"><span>你是否也想希望通过研习一门乐器，提高个人气质与音乐素养？</span></span></p>\n\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t\t<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\"><span>你是否也想要学习古筝演奏，感受古筝的清越悠扬？</span></span></p>\n\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\"><span>你是否也想感受古筝这一乐器的深厚内涵和底蕴？</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"http://tuan.hujiang.com/tuangou/p954/?source=499\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201307/c6497f4a-a0ee-47b0-be88-cce5977bf765_04.jpg\" /></a></p>\n\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\"><span>本课程由中国杰出古筝</span><span><span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px;\">表演艺术</span></span><span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px;\">家</span></span></span><span>，中央音乐学院古筝专业导</span><span>师</span>袁莎老师<span>亲自授课。</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t\t<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\"><span>课程颠覆了大家对学琴神秘高难复杂的心理障碍，<strong>简化入门技巧，让入门更简易。</strong></span></span></p>\n\t\t<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t\t<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\"><span>并将高高在上的经典名曲改编成适合初学者的入门教材，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt;\">让每个人都能轻松快乐学习古筝。</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"http://tuan.hujiang.com/tuangou/p954/?source=499\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201307/c6497f4a-a0ee-47b0-be88-cce5977bf765_05.jpg\" /></a></p>\n\t\t<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t\t<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\"><strong>本课程共15课时，从零基础开始，</strong>通过<span>《笑傲江湖》、《春江花月夜》、《茉莉花》、《菊花台》、《青花瓷》等</span>歌曲演奏技法的分解，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\">让同学们完全掌握5大基本技法，轻松完成古筝入门学习。</span></span></p>\n\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\"><span>袁莎老师还为课程中的每首乐曲精心制作出<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px;\">MIDI</span>伴奏音乐，</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\"><span>帮助大家更有乐趣地练习，即使是初学者，也能<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">完成</span>极具表现力的独奏演出！</span></span></p>\n\t\t<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 6px; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(62, 76, 144); border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px;\">\n\t\t\t\t<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\"><strong>琴棋书画，样样精通！</strong></span></p>\n\t\t\t<a href=\"http://tuan.hujiang.com/tuangou/p954/?source=499\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201307/c6497f4a-a0ee-47b0-be88-cce5977bf765_06.jpg\" style=\"height: 301px; width: 450px;\" /></a></div>\n\t</div>\n\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; border: 0px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 102);\">爱它悠扬婉转，更爱它深厚底蕴！</strong></span></p>\n\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t&nbsp;</p>\n\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t<a href=\"http://tuan.hujiang.com/tuangou/p954/?source=499\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>现在就去团&gt;&gt;</strong></a></p>\n</div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p515431/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p515431\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\